---

<Layout title="wrath • home">
  <article>
    <small class="text-sm text-zinc-500">
      IPA&nbsp; /raTH/ — extreme anger 😼
    </small>

    <p>
      Hello 🙋‍♂️ my name is <strong>Ausath</strong>, or <strike>wrath</strike> <i>(ign)</i>. 
